      <ul class="docs-list">
        <li><strong>Missing subpath exports</strong> — Added <code>./cta-banner</code> and <code>./input</code> to <code>package.json</code> exports so <code>import '@arclux/arc-ui/cta-banner'</code> and <code>import '@arclux/arc-ui/input'</code> resolve correctly for tree-shaking.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="tier-heading">Cleanup</h3>
      <ul class="docs-list">
        <li><strong>Removed tier exports</strong> — Dropped <code>./content</code>, <code>./feedback</code>, <code>./navigation</code>, <code>./layout</code>, and <code>./shared</code> tier-level subpath exports. Use per-component imports (<code>@arclux/arc-ui/button</code>) or the barrel (<code>@arclux/arc-ui</code>) instead.</li>
      </ul>

    </section>

    <section id="v1-8-1">
      <h2 class="docs-heading">v1.8.1 — Tree-Shaking Bugfix</h2>
      <arc-divider align="left" variant="line-gradient" style="max-width:48px;margin-bottom:var(--space-md)"></arc-divider>

      <p class="docs-text">
        Fixes named barrel imports like <code>import {'{'} ArcButton {'}'} from '@arclux/arc-ui'</code>
        being tree-shaken away by Vite/Rollup, causing components to silently not render.
      </p>

      <h3 class="tier-heading">Bug Fixes</h3>
